Field_DynamicState: Set the dynamic state of a particle (static, dynamic, kinematic...)
Field_LinearForce: Add a vector field to the particles linear force.
Field_ExternalClusterStrain: Apply an external strain over the particles. If this strain is over the internal one, the cluster will break.
Field_Kill: Disable the particles for which the field will be higher than 0.
Field_LinearVelocity: Add a vector field to the particles linear velocity.
Field_AngularVelociy: Add a vector field to the particles angular velocity.
Field_AngularTorque: Add a vector field to the particles angular torque.
Field_InternalClusterStrain: Add a strain field to the particles internal one.
Field_DisableThreshold: Disable the particles if their linear and angular velocity are less than the threshold.
Field_SleepingThreshold: Set particles in sleeping mode if their linear and angular velocity are less than the threshold.
Field_PositionStatic: Add a position constraint to the particles to remain static
Field_PositionAnimated: Add a position constraint to the particles to follow its kinematic position
Field_PositionTarget: Add a position constraint to the particles to follow a target position
Field_DynamicConstraint: Add the particles to a spring constraint holding them together
Field_ActivateDisabled: Activate all the disabled particles for which the field value will be 0
Field_InitialLinearVelocity: Set the geometry collection initial linear velocity
Field_InitialAngularVelocity: Set the geometry collection initial angular velocity
Field_LinearImpulse: Add a vector field affecting the particles linear impulse.
